          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely grate the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
